18:14.240 --> 18:20.640
will always have some gates that we can't implement this way. And so we need to look for alternative gadgets. By the

162
18:20.640 --> 18:27.360
eastern canal theorem, we know that it's not possible to implement a universal set of quantum gates transversely even

